DESC_SETTINGS: Include games in the include.txt even if the rom does not exist.
Defines whether the items in a collection will be sorted alphabetically
Defines whether the roms directory should be searched hierarchically. There is a performance hit by enabling this, so only use it when needed.

Specifies which launcher is used when a game is selected from the menu (reads from launchers/<launcher name>.conf). This value can be overwritten per game by putting the launcher name in a single line .conf file in collections/<collection name>/launchers/<game name>.conf.

Specifies the meta file used in the meta.db to pull additional information like manufacturer, year, genre, etc. from
